import React from 'react'
import {
    SimpleGrid,
    Box,
    Text
} from '@chakra-ui/react'

function DashboardMain(props){
    const dataItems = props.dataItems;
    const dataItem = dataItems.map((sm) =>{
        <Box
            display='flex'
            flexDirection='column'
            justifyContent='center'
            alignItems="center"
            borderTop="5px solid hsl(208, 92%, 53%)"
            h='180px'
            bgColor='gray.200'>
                <Text
                mb={2}>
                    Hola 1
                    </Text>
                <Text
                mb={2}>
                    Hola 2
                </Text>
                <Text
                mb={2}>
                    Hola 3
                </Text>
                <Text
                mb={2}>
                    Hola 4
                </Text>
        </Box>
    })

    return (
        <>
            <SimpleGrid columns={4} spacing={10}>
                {dataItem}
            </SimpleGrid>
        </>
    )
}

export default DashboardMain
